 "introduction_text": "<h2>Periodic Donation Agreement</h2>\n<p>Set up a 5-year periodic donation agreement to maximize your tax benefits. Under Dutch ANBI regulations, periodic donations are fully tax-deductible without threshold or maximum limits.</p>\n<div class='alert alert-info'>\n<strong>Benefits of a Periodic Donation Agreement:</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>100% tax deductible (no threshold or maximum)</li>\n<li>Fixed commitment for better planning</li>\n<li>Automatic payment options available</li>\n<li>Official documentation for tax purposes</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
